{
  "stem": "5654.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being 120 boys and girls-- if I can remember, there was one director who was in charge, the headmaster.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were-- we were-- we had so many groups.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was assigned to a-- to a group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was run by Mr. and-- Monsieur et Madame Dybnis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dybnis.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "D-Y-B-N-I-S.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dybnis.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Miriam-- that was her first name-- and Henri.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, when Henri Dybnis came to our home, they got married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The two got married.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a big wedding there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, not a big wedding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To us, it was a big wedding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so they were like-- virtually like parents to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my group with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- How many in your group?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our group, we must have been about 20, 30 people. 30 boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so what-- because you see, not all of us could go, let's say, on the excursion.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[COUGHS] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were too many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to make smaller group, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to be careful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because outside the home in the country, every now and again we would see a German patrol coming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow, they were always on horses or walking, the German patrol, you see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So by the 1943, it got very-- it became very bad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In September.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came in 19-- end of '39, '40.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed in Brout-Vernet right up to 19-- April, 1943.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow, we were notified-- the, the headmaster was notified that the Germans were coming to pick us up the following day.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Please get out quickly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we left everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we split into various groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My group was still with, with the Dybnis.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
